title: BONUS: Best of HEY BABE! | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe!
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
Chris and Sal took the week off so here is a BEST of HEY BABE!!! A collection of fan favorite moments from the first year of HEY BABE! Chris tries pork chops for the first time and Sal tries Cinnabon. Sal brings his dead fish on the podcast! The babes break world records! The oldest living human becomes the shows unofficial mascot. THE STATEN ISLAND BOYZ learn about 2 strange rappers. The shit queen brings some HEAT to the first live Hey Babe. The woman with the biggest mouth stops by and the babes put stuff in her mouth YASSSSS!  The babes will be back next week!The merch is out now babes!!! Check it out on the store tab of Sals Website - salvulcanocomedy.com
Rate us on iTunes!
